Business Information
															The group's principal activities are to design, construct and market homes and to provide financial services. It operates through two segments namely, homebuilding and financial services. The homebuilding segment designs, constructs and markets single family detached homes, townhouses and attached condominium apartments. The group builds and sells homes in New Jersey, Pennsylvania, New York, Virginia, Maryland, North Carolina, Texas and California. Financial services segment provides mortgage loans and title insurance to its homebuilding customers. In 2003, the group acquired parkside homes, brighton homes, great western homes and windward homes and Florida homebuilder on 06-Nov-2003.   
															






                       
