Why Choose Us

We are a company devoted to buildingcommunities of excellence.
K. Hovnanian® Homes is heir to a history of solid success, financial strength, award-winning standards of homebuilding quality and an authentic commitment to customer satisfaction.









Our History



































Why Choose Us


We are a company devoted to building communities of excellence.

The value of a priceless heritage is measured by the purpose and dedication of its heirs. K. Hovnanian® Homes is heir to a history of solid success, financial strength, award-winning standards of homebuilding quality and an authentic commitment to customer satisfaction. Sharing this heritage with you, as your homebuilder, is both our mission and our privilege.















Financial Strength

It is important to know that the  company building your home has built a sound legacy of business success.  Hovnanian Enterprises®, Inc. began trading on the New York Stock Exchange in 2001 and has continually grown in financial strength to rank among the top ten homebuilding companies in America.  This strength assures you that your home and neighborhood are the results of our dedication and commitment.






Financial Strength

"Like the deep roots of an old oak tree, our financial strength has demonstrated profound stability and uncompromising growth." 
Ara K. Hovnanian

Your life has taught you that experience matters.  That's why K. Hovnanian® Homes' legacy of homebuilding makes a difference.  For over fifty years, we've shown how a family-run, publicly-traded business can flourish when an outstanding job is done.  

As we create communities nationwide, we study how people's lives change to gain a personal understanding of our customer's needs.  That's why our communities feel so fulfilling, familiar, fresh and new.  
 








Homebuyer Stories




ALL STATES

















The K. Hovnanian®
Advantage


Heritage

To succeed for more than 50 years as a company, it helps to have a clear vision of what you stand for. Back in 1959, our Founder, Kevork S. Hovnanian gave us just that when he created K. Hovnanian® Homes.  We know that your home is the foundation of your family's lifestyle, and we honor that philosophy by making sure your new home meets your every desire.  We are especially pleased by the number of our homeowners who have purchased their second, third or subsequent K. Hovnanian® home - an honor that underscores their confidence in us.  Now in its second generation of family leadership, K. Hovnanian® Homes continues to be  known as "The First Name in Lasting Value®."






The Importance of
Customer Satisfaction


Commitment

It is our promise to pursue excellence in everything we do to meet our homebuyers' expectations. Our Associates are available to answer questions and make the homebuying experience a positive one.  We strive to always delight our customers with our products and services.






It's All About
Choice


Variety

In towns and cities throughout America, we have been translating ideas into blueprints and dreams into homes. Utilizing state-of-the-art technologies, construction methods and materials, our experienced architects, designers and  planners create homes to meet your every need. From the big city attitude of a dazzling urban retreat, to beautiful suburban townhome neighborhoods, charming single family home communities and the ultimate resort-at-home active adult lifestyle, we have exciting home designs to suit your taste, budget and desires.






The Perfect
Location


Home

You can customize a home but you can't change the location. Where you live is as important as how you live. Our land acquisition specialists search for the best areas to plan communities that are conveniently located and take advantage of the natural terrain. We build homes in the school districts you want for your children, close to shopping, medical facilities, entertainment and cultural activities. For over 50 years, families have trusted K. Hovnanian® to create the perfect place to call home. 






Lasting
Quality & Value 


Timeless

Our relationships with industry professionals let us purchase quality materials, in quantity, from the most reliable sources. This means that you get a superior quality home at the best possible value.  Our reputation is proof that superior quality and value are the cornerstones of success. This is why K. Hovnanian® Homes® is now, and has been for over fifty years, "The First Name In Lasting Value®."






Solid
Relationships


Integrity

From the beginning it has always been about relationships. Much of the company's foundation was built on trust and a handshake.  Mr. Hovnanian always believed that building a good relationship was essential to building a good home.  Whether you’re a homebuyer, contractor, real estate agent or vendor, this simple message stands at the center of everything we do.






It  All Comes Down to
Reputation


Impeccable

In 1959 our Founder, Kevork S. Hovnanian (pictured with his son, Ara), came to a new land with a dream: to build a home for his family, and for all families seeking a better life. Although we were greatly saddened by his passing in 2009, his dream inspires us every day, and his integrity and legacy continue to guide us as we come together to build homes and communities for each and every family who puts their trust in us. With communities in over 17 states, K. Hovnanian® Homes® has established a reputation as one of the nation’s most respected homebuilders.  Whether you are  purchasing your first home, moving up to a larger residence to accommodate your growing family, seeking an upscale mid-rise condominium or country estate, or considering a new home on your own land, K. Hovnanian® will help you find the home of your dreams.






There's Nothing More Important than
Family


Yours

We build your home as we would build our own, with the utmost care, excellent materials and according to exacting standards. We consider everyone we come into contact with to be an essential part of our family. This includes not just the homebuyers we serve, but our Associates, trade partners and the communities in which we build. Now in its second generation of family leadership, it has been our privilege to build over 310,000 homes for families just like yours across the Nation. It would be our honor to do the same for you.















We Give Back

K. Hovnanian® Companies, LLC
Donates $1 Million to
9/11 Relief Efforts

On behalf of its Associates and business partners, Hovnanian Enterprises, Inc. committed $1 million toward relief efforts for those impacted by the terrorist attacks. The Company was proud to say their Associates and business partners also volunteered to make contributions toward the relief effort as well. 






State-of-the-Art
Heart Center

In January of 2010, a state-of-the-art Heart Center at New York Presbyterian Hospital/Columbia opened. The Clinical Cardiology Center on the 4th floor of the Heart Center building was made possible by a gift from the Hovnanian family. The new facility provides comprehensive and unmatched services in heart care, making it one of the top heart care centers in the world.






Riverview Medical Center's
K. Hovnanian® Pavilion

The creation of Riverview's Alton A. Hovnanian Emergency Care Center began early in 2003, requiring a new wing be added to the existing hospital. The wing, called the K. Hovnanian® Pavilion, houses a new and expanded Critical Care Center. Both the Emergency Care Center and the Critical Care Center include the most advanced patient monitoring technology in the area as well as vast improvements in both the size of the treatment rooms and comfort of environment. 






K. Hovnanian
Children's Hospital

In 2006, the children's hospital located in Jersey Shore University Medical Center in Neptune, NJ, became the first state-designated children's hospital in the bi-county area and was renamed K. Hovnanian Children's Hospital in honor of Mr. and Mrs. Kevork S. Hovnanian's generosity. The designation recognizes years of advanced pediatric clinical care services provided by Jersey Shore. In 2008, the Children's Hospital expanded to include a teen lounge, a satellite nursing station, and additional pediatric rooms, bringing its total number of beds up to 31 (plus a six bed pediatric intensive care unit). The remainder of the rooms received an aesthetic overhaul, with family friendly features, such as flat-screen televisions.






K. Hovnanian
Pediatric Department

In the summer of 2009, K. Hovnanian Children's Hospital opened a dedicated pediatric Emergency Department as part of Jersey Shore University Hospital's $300 million transformation project. The emergency department now has a separate entrance and triage area, as well as 10-12 pediatric beds.









